reviewText:
I enjoyed this Blue Ray record for a while, then my son invited me to the concert in Anaheim recently. It was pretty good.
I am purchasing this Blue Ray second time - for my son.
Great set list, the band sounds great.
Without any doubt, this is the best of all the Depeche Mode concerts.  Their performance is first rate, and the camera work & editing are outstanding.  Highly recommended.
Great DVD!!!! A must have for the Depeche Mode fan.
